# Portions Copyright (c) 1997 by Stan Barber.  
# Portions Copyright (c) 1997 by Kent Landfield.  
# Portions Copyright (c) 1991, 1992, 1993, 1994, 1995, 1996, 1997  
#   Free Software Foundation, Inc.    
